headline: Ameren Missouri delivers generation projects that support residential customers, businesses and diversifies portfolio
summary: Today, Ameren Missouri announced 500 megawatts (MW) of new solar generation, representing a total investment of approximately $950 million, are now serving customers. Combined, the three facilities are anticipated to generate energy sufficient to power 92,000 homes annually.
